Post Installation
================

- With the Applet

1. Add the applet (GlobalMenu MatePanelApplet) to the panel.
2. Enable the Gtk Plugin from the preference window of the applet.

- With Mate Panel

Enable the following mateconf keys via mateconf-editor
 apps/mate_settings_daemon/gtk_modules/globalmenu-mate-panel
Add Panel Menu Bar to the top panel if it is not already there

